   &mt RGUI N1     &kp N2    &kp N3    &kp N4    &kp N5        &kp N6    &kp N7     &kp N8    &kp N9     &mt RALT N0
   &mt LALT GRAVE  &trans    &kp LBKT  &kp RBKT  &trans        &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN   &kp UP    &kp RIGHT  &mt RGUI SQT
   &mt LSHFT TAB   &trans    &trans    &trans    &trans        &kp BKSP  &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL &kp SPACE  &mt RSHFT BSLH
